c CARDS 8 -> (8+n−1) — POLYGON BOUNDARY POINTS (format 2F10.0)
c theta = latitude of boundary point (deg)
c phi   = longitude of boundary point (deg)
c
c Rules:
c - Points form a closed polygon
c - First point is NOT repeated at the end
c - Longitude spacing must match hphi
